Global Structural Core Materials Market Insights
Structural Core Materials Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.4 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Structural Core Materials Market Overview
The global structural core materials market was valued at USD 2.5 billion in 2023 and is projected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.5% from 2024 to 2030. This growth is driven by the increasing demand for lightweight materials across various industries, including aerospace, automotive, wind energy, and marine. The need for materials that offer high strength-to-weight ratios and durability is propelling the adoption of structural core materials. Additionally, advancements in manufacturing technologies and a growing emphasis on sustainability are contributing to market expansion. Source

